*"200-0919-003 REV A1" is etched onto one particular AP's board. *"200-0920-001 REV3" is silkscreened on the wireless module in the FCC photos. :This module is highly homologous to the [[Intel PRO/Wireless 5000 LAN 3A Mini PCI Adapter|Intel PRO/Wireless 5000 LAN 3A Mini PCI]].

==Probable used PSU(s)== The FCC test report specifies the '''YHI''' YC-1018-S05-U :as the power supply used (5V, 2.5A).
